data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This well-maintained remodeled residence offers a spacious and inviting atmosphere. The large open floor plan with previous additions seamlessly connects the main living spaces, creating a welcoming environment for gatherings. The primary bedroom is a versatile space that can be located on either the main floor or the second level. With 4 bedrooms and 3.5 baths, this home provides ample space for a growing family or accommodating guests. Newly resurfaced hardwood floors on the main level, add a touch of elegance to the home. The natural warmth of the hardwood creates a cozy and timeless ambiance throughout the living areas. Many upgrades including Lower Level HVAC, New Hot Water Heater, New Roof, New Carpet on Stairs, New Garage Door, Granite Countertops in Kitchen, Widened Front Driveway, Extended Back Deck, and Stained/Painted Fence. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning property your own. Schedule a viewing today!
